name: HongKongGuide
0:
”Alexa, open Hong Kong Guide.”
”Alexa, open Hong Kong Guide and tell me the local news.”
”Alexa, ask Hong Kong Guide for top five things to do.”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: hong kong guide
des:
This Hong Kong Guide is a useful little app that provides travelers with suggestions on places to visit, things to do, and local news while visiting the spectacular city of Hong Kong.
Ask Alexa things such as: Give me an attraction. Tell me about Hong Kong. Tell me the top five things to do. Tell me the local news.
Give this app a try on your next trip to Hong Kong!
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
